WEBVTT

00:08:58.875 --> 00:09:00.518
And that's my real point.

00:09:00.542 --> 00:09:03.434
I'm not just here
to show you my film footage.

00:09:03.458 --> 00:09:05.476
I'm here to remind us all

00:09:05.500 --> 00:09:07.726
that life is really just a lesson

00:09:07.750 --> 00:09:10.809
in finding the balance
between fear and courage.

00:09:10.833 --> 00:09:15.643
And understanding what is
and what isn't a good idea.

00:09:15.667 --> 00:09:16.893
(Laughter)

00:09:16.917 --> 00:09:18.643
Life is already scary,

00:09:18.667 --> 00:09:22.393
so for our dreams to come true,
we need to be brave.

00:09:22.417 --> 00:09:23.768
In facing my fears

00:09:23.792 --> 00:09:26.393
and finding the courage
to push through them,

00:09:26.417 --> 00:09:30.101
I swear my life has been extraordinary.